biography.text: A globally renowned DJ and producer, Netsky has become a leading figure in the Drum & Bass scene, captivating audiences from Coachella to Glastonbury. In 2017, he launched his Netsky & Friends brand, headlining Tomorrowland's Mainstage and curating stages across Europe. With four studio albums featuring collaborations with Lil Wayne and David Guetta, plus remixes for Dua Lipa and Ed Sheeran, his sound has earned him numerous accolades, including being the highest-ranked Drum & Bass DJ in DJ Mag's Top 100. His 2020 album Second Nature led to sold-out Glasshouse shows, and in 2023, he continued to push boundaries with his hit single Barricades (With Rita Ora).
